    <item>
      <title>特朗普的财政部长人选将与 Thune 及关键参议员会面商讨任命事宜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/bessent-to-meet-thune-key-senators-on-treasury-confirmation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长提名人斯科特·贝森特 (Scott Bessent) 计划本周晚些时候与即将上任的参议院共和党领袖约翰·图恩 (John Thune) 和其他主要参议员会面，开始为确认听证会做准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/bessent-to-meet-thune-key-senators-on-treasury-confirmation</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 17:18:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克总统任命莱特拉为新任总检察长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/mozambique-president-appoints-letela-new-attorney-general</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫桑比克总统菲利佩·纽西任命阿梅里科·莱特拉为新任总检察长，全国正在等待宪法委员会对十月份有争议的选举结果的批准。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/mozambique-president-appoints-letela-new-attorney-general</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 17:15:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登作为首位访问安哥拉的美国领导人大力宣传洛比托计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/biden-touts-lobito-project-as-first-us-leader-to-visit-angola</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登周二会见安哥拉总统若昂·洛伦索时，大力宣传其政府与安哥拉的关系，包括投资一条铁路，以将关键矿产运送到整个非洲大陆。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/biden-touts-lobito-project-as-first-us-leader-to-visit-angola</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 14:19:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国总统尹永康宣布戒严 令人震惊的政治举措</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/south-korea-s-yoon-declares-martial-law-in-emergency-address</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈周二宣布实施戒严，此举震惊了选民、议员和投资者。他声称，在韩国政治裂痕势必明显加深的情况下，这一高风险举措将阻止反对派试图瘫痪他的政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/south-korea-s-yoon-declares-martial-law-in-emergency-address</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 13:47:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国以报复性金属禁令加剧美国贸易紧张局势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/china-bans-germanium-gallium-exports-to-us-in-tit-for-tat-move</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统拜登领导的政府加大对北京的技术限制后，中国采取针锋相对的举措，禁止进口多种高科技和军事用途的材料，此举加剧了与美国的贸易紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/china-bans-germanium-gallium-exports-to-us-in-tit-for-tat-move</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 08:21:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
